Proof-of-Patience ($PoP) Coin: The Citadel Plan

Litepaper v0.7 — June 2025

Introduction

Proof-of-Patience ($PoP) Coin is a Cardano-based utility token designed to restore fairness to limited drops and digital collectibles. By leveraging the power of blockchain and a unique staking mechanism, $PoP aims to give real fans a fair shot and make large-scale botting economically unprofitable.

Problem Statement

  • Limited drops are often dominated by bots, leaving real fans frustrated.
  • Current anti-bot solutions are either ineffective or create friction for genuine users.
  • There is a need for a transparent, decentralized, and fair system.

Solution Overview

  • Stake $PoP Coin to prove your patience and commitment.
  • Stakers receive a fair, weighted chance in limited drops.
  • Token burns and fees make botting unprofitable at scale.
  • Community governance ensures ongoing fairness and transparency.

Tokenomics

  • Total Supply: 100,000,000 $PoP (fixed, no hidden minting)
  • Deflationary: Token burns on every drop and transaction fee
  • Distribution: 60% Community, 20% Team, 10% Partnerships, 10% Reserve

How It Works

  1. Stake: Users stake $PoP to participate in drops.
  2. Random Draw: Each staker gets a fair, weighted chance based on their stake.
  3. Burn & Fee: A portion of tokens is burned and a fee is collected to fund development and community rewards.

Governance

  • Transition to full community governance via DAO.
  • Major decisions (e.g., drop rules, fee rates) are voted on by $PoP holders.

Roadmap

  1. Q2 2025: Launch $PoP Coin, website, and initial staking app
  2. Q3 2025: First limited drops, community building, and token burns
  3. Q4 2025: DAO launch, full community governance, and expanded partnerships

Transparency

  • All smart contracts and tokenomics are public and open source.
  • Regular updates and transparent reporting to the community.

Conclusion

$PoP Coin is more than just a token—it's a movement to bring fairness, transparency, and real fandom back to digital drops. Join us and help build The Citadel Plan!

Contact & Community: Join our Discord
